 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#how-to-track-competitor-rankings-at-an-enterprise-scale"&gt;How to Track Competitor Rankings at an Enterprise Scale&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#frequently-asked-questions-about-enterprise-rank-tracking-software"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions About Enterprise Rank Tracking Software&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
